bug 2228: untaint the paths processed by rel2abs()

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5638 | felicity | 2003-07-20 15:34:12 -0700 (Sun, 20 Jul 2003) | 3 lines

bug 2244: Make the Razor modules not load when first loading M::SA::Dns,
