r5616 | msquadrat | 2003-07-14 07:42:18 -0700 (Mon, 14 Jul 2003) | 2 lines

Pod::Usage 1.0, shipped with Perl 5.005_03, has a weird dependency on Pod::Text 2.0 which never ever existed. The next working version seems to be 1.10, so that's the minimum we require (Perl 5.6.1 ships 1.13).

