r5546 | felicity | 2003-06-20 10:54:51 -0700 (Fri, 20 Jun 2003) | 6 lines

bug 2092: The header report _REPORT_ has a newline at the end of each
line, but the _process_header function expects the string to not have
a newline at the end as it adds one when putting the header into the
message.  Let's trim off trailing newlines from anything going through
_process_header.

