r5504 | felicity | 2003-06-13 17:08:32 -0700 (Fri, 13 Jun 2003) | 5 lines

bug 1558: if there is no message-id in the message we're trying to learn,
generate one based on the sha1() hash of the Date, the first add (last
listed) Received header, and the first N bytes of the body (1k or 1/2
message length, whichever is smaller).

