r4873 | felicity | 2003-03-27 12:36:08 -0800 (Thu, 27 Mar 2003) | 5 lines

bug 1632: Razor modifies %ENV so we tried to use a local() to make a
temp version, which works, but kills %ENV for the Razor code as well.
So now we'll let the helper_mode functions handle backing up/restoring
%ENV as appropriate.

