improving the useful range of hits for this test (the same exact FP
problem seems to affect SUSPICIOUS_RECIPS)
also add T_SORTED_RECIPIENTS test for testing (an extension of the
new suspect recipients code since much of the similarity seems to be
the result of sorting)

