r4142 | felicity | 2002-12-23 20:29:44 -0800 (Mon, 23 Dec 2002) | 12 lines

bug 786: DEAR_SOMEBODY and DEAR_SOMETHING have a bit of overlap.
Created DEAR_SOMEBODY replacement meta rule to see if we can clear it up.
DEAR_SOMEBODY has a fairly bad S/O rating anyway, so we may just end up
removing it.

