r3677 | felicity | 2002-10-14 08:50:44 -0700 (Mon, 14 Oct 2002) | 12 lines

Added a new phrase to EXCUSE_10 that increases the spam hits with no
new FPs for me:

  1.344    3.262    0.008    1.00    0.71    1.00  T_EXCUSE_10
  1.286    3.120    0.008    1.00    0.71    0.33  EXCUSE_10

Also added 2 new test rules.  They catch a few FN spams I have, but are
low matching overall.  Have to see how they do for everyone else:

  0.044    0.106    0.000    1.00    0.64    1.00  T_EXCUSE_25
  0.039    0.095    0.000    1.00    0.63    1.00  T_LEAVE_ADDR

