r3640 | felicity | 2002-10-08 16:45:52 -0700 (Tue, 08 Oct 2002) | 7 lines

$self->{html}{min_img_ratio} is "inf" by default, which gets checked
via "<" which causes perl to error.  Added a check that allows
"inf" to do the right thing.

Added a rule to check for % encoding in URIs that don't need to be
there (characters that don't need encoding via RFC).

