Fixed .cvsignore's for Debian building

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2577 | duncf | 2002-06-20 19:46:50 -0700 (Thu, 20 Jun 2002) | 7 lines

Adding support for building debian packages from CVS.
Requires: debhelper (>> 4.0), devscripts, dpkg-dev

Run from top level directory, debian/build.pl and then run
dpkg-buildpackage as usual (remember you need the -b option, source
uploads are impossible) or use debian/build.pl -d

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2576 | quinlan | 2002-06-20 12:38:43 -0700 (Thu, 20 Jun 2002) | 5 lines

