------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2569 | duncf | 2002-06-19 19:19:36 -0700 (Wed, 19 Jun 2002) | 7 lines

migrate_cfs is no longer needed.
migrate_cfs is a bashism.
migrate_cfs impedes a corner case of packageability.
Makefiles should never touch ANYTHING outside the build directory.
I'd remove migrate_cfs entirely, but we might find some clueless user
that hasn't upgraded yet.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
