------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2310 | climent | 2002-04-21 03:23:00 -0700 (Sun, 21 Apr 2002) | 6 lines

This commit introduces basic modifications:
 * SA is not a filter per se. It is an scoring mechanism
 * Thus we should not try to match exact lines in spammers but instead to
   recognize basic rules used by them.
 * Consecuently the rules have been modified a bit to express this idea.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
